      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know there are numbers i can call but it feels so empty. like, it doesn't actually change the fact that i'm drowning. the stress is just constant and i'm so tired of fighting to keep my head above water every single day. it's just... exhausting to keep trying when nothing ever gets better.",
